== Itihas ==
Poilim ek chovk koso bandlolo, Taka  Praça de Sete Janelas (Sat zonelacho chovk) hea nanvan vollkhotale.Tem nanv protixttit Goenchea Pulis mukhealoiechea imaroti velean dilolem, zaka donui vattamnim ani provesant sat zonelam asat. Imarotik poilim fokot tollmozlo ani dor poile malliek sat zonelamcho sancho aslo.<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZtZ4_irUPp0</ref> 1843 vorsa, porakromi veokti Putugez senapoti Afonso de Albuquerque hachi gumtti aslolea bandavollint Moidanant, ek murti ghalpant aili.Lokhnacheo patteo ani tollpache khambe hea iadostikek Adlea Goenchea S. Domingos konventant savn haddlole, oxem mhonnttat. College of St. Thomas Aquinas hache koddlean, ji  Conceição dongurlecher asli  thoinchean gumtteche khambe ani sthomb aile. Albuquerque-achi murti sthaplea uprant, chovkak Praça Afonso de Albuquerque<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZtZ4_irUPp0</ref> nanvan vollkhopant ailem.

== Soddvonne uprant ==
Goenchem samilikoronn zalea uprant, Albuquerque-achi murti lokamni gumttechea asona voili denvoili.<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZtZ4_irUPp0</ref>  Albuquerque-achi murti  ABharoti Pornamvoll Sorvekxonnacba Songrohaloient  Adlea Goeant halovpant aili.<ref>https://www.goa-tourism.com/GTDC-holidays/see-museum-archaeological-museum-of-goa.htm</ref><ref>http://www.goaholidayhomes.com/information/the-azad-maidan.html</ref> Famad Goenkar svotontrsoinik Dr. Tristão de Bragança Cunha hachem ek pitullchem osthikolos tea zagear sthap’pant ailem.<ref>http://www.heraldgoa.in/Goa/Panjim/Memorial-for-freedom-fighters-is-resting-place-for-beggars-and-stray-dogs/89809.html</ref>

== Hutatmeachi Iadgiri ==
Ek hutatmeachi iadgiri  Moidanacher  Svotontr Soinikechea Sonsthen lokachea denngeamni, Goenchea Soddvonnechea chollvollent<ref>http://www.navhindtimes.in/martyrs-memorial-an-icon-of-the-resistance-and-brotherhood/</ref> zannim aplo jiv teag kelo tachea ugddasak bandpant aili. Iadgiri ek unch bandavoll zachi tenkxi ek char-hatanchem bandkaml dakhoita.Char-hatanchi bandavollik ek monoro modem ani hea hatancher asa. Char-hatanchi bandavoll Bharotachea charui konxeantlea svotontr soinikachem hea Goenchea Soddvonnechea chollvollint vantto ghevop dakhol korta, zorui monoreachi bandavoll gobor, mhonnche hea svotontr soinikancho teag dakhoita.<ref>http://www.navhindtimes.in/panaji-a-city-honours-remembers-its-past/</ref> Iadgirichem onavoronn 23 Mars 1973 vorsa zalem jem  Naiob Rajiopal Kunhiraman Palat Candeth zannem Bharoti Xoxostr Fouje udexim Goenchem samilikoronn Dezembr 1961 vorsa kelolem.<ref>http://www.navhindtimes.in/martyrs-memorial-an-icon-of-the-resistance-and-brotherhood/</ref> The memorial was unveiled on 23 March 1973 by Lieutenant general Kunhiraman Palat Candeth, who had led the Indian Armed Forces' annexation of Goa in December 1961. Ek koddvem jem kovi Balakrishna Bhagwant Borkar hannem rochlam tem tea iadgirint kontrailam hea porim:
 
